Stunning, high resolution weather maps with multiple layers of advanced weather information including precipitation type radar in Europe, radar forecasts, heat maps, lightning strikes and cloud cover forecasts.	Beach Weather with UV Index and water temperatures for the Mediterranean, Caribbean and other popular holiday destinations.
